    "body" : "<p>I am using Intellij Idea 2017 and I got into the same problem. What solved the problem for me was to simply </p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>close the project in intelliJ </li>\n<li>File -> New -> project from existing resources </li>\n<li>use Import from external model (if any) </li>\n<li>open the project again. </li>\n</ol>\n"
